data.description: This one is ready to move in! Clean and cozy, one level, all-brick rancher located in a quiet neighborhood setting. Three Spacious bedrooms with a split bedroom floor plan, two full baths, ceiling fans in every room, and a private and level backyard.  All appliances and lawn mower in garage convey!  This property is well maintained, convenient to parks and shopping, and waiting for you to call it home!
